Yes Which kit? (if not sure: Genomics Core will provide this information)	 Would you like the CCBB to provide data analysis?	Yes We highly recommend completing this section in anticipation of future GEO submissions	 Goal of the Project	Identify genes that are differentially regulated in murine chondrocytes treated by 2 doses of pollutants Details of requested bioinformatics analyses	Identify genes that are differentially regulated in murine chondrocytes treated by 2 doses of pollutants:  a.	compared DE genes between CONTROL and DOSE 1 (MIX 2X)"	 "b.	compared DE genes between CONTROL and DOSE 2 (MIX 20X)"	 "c.	compared DE genes between DOSE 1 (MIX 2X) and DOSE 2 (MIX 20X)"	 	 It is 4 independent experiments (S300-S303-S304-S305). Each experiment is composed of CONTROL-DOSE 1- DOSE2 come from the same culture of chondrocytes. The analyze is paired by experiment if possible.
